ystem-font, system-ui, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">1&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">为什么要学《易经》？</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"></span></strong></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">「人到三十，不能再靠努力，而是运气。」</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);">所谓运，就是赢面和机会。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">计算过赢面之后，再拼尽全力去行动，这也是曾国藩的心法。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">曾国藩《易经》不离手，把《易经》里面的智慧融汇在人生选择里。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 170, 214);">对儒家大德来说，《易经》里面的智慧，不是用来占卜和迷信，而是用于计算赢面。《易经》用二进制算法，演变成64幕剧本，解决了计算赢面的问题。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">曾国藩平时就喜欢不厌其烦地对弟弟曾国荃说「日中则仄，月满则亏」的「盈虚消息之理」。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appXJ0BcLXr3494/image/ueditor/97489900_1553662309.cn/mmbiz_jpg/3mfm1joonf1oodf4eqfs3zgicyibxvhxin6pkl2q0oi5k7w2nek3k01cbgnm5mfl4zmmxhqhmjm7z2tvficquapca/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 347px; width: 556px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">打胜仗后，曾国藩告诉他，「屯」卦（意指饱满充盈）之后是「需」卦（意指等待时机），接下来我们应该全身而退。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">此时曾家兄弟已经创下不世功勋，消灭太平天国，双双封侯伯爵位，他们接下来的赢面已经很小了。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;">汉人不许封王，他们上面只有一个公爵。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">为一个小空间去冒险，有什么意思呢？这个时候全身而退，低调行事，反而可以蓄积力量，等待下一次机会，让危险变成焦点。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appXJ0BcLXr3494/image/ueditor/7586800_1553662310.cn/mmbiz_jpg/3mfm1joonf3iatlceyy0qdax2imsanjcasqvgrtxnricjhamawibkicuea5ydicymkh51cwzx6jwzzumxovziq2vpyw/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">曾国藩还讲过「乾卦」的道理：</span>从第五爻「飞龙在天」，到第六爻「亢龙有悔」，说的也是类似的意思。都已经飞龙在天了，上面没有空间了。还是别那么亢奋了，收敛收敛，赢面更大。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">说到底，会算赢面的人，有更大的机会能成为大赢家。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="color: rgb(61, 170, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">《易经》的64卦，每一卦的六个爻辞合起来，刚好是一个故事剧本。</em><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 170, 214);"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">在这64卦里，有很多这样的故事。</em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 170, 214);"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appXJ0BcLXr3494/image/ueditor/22629600_1553662310.cn/mmbiz_jpg/3mfm1joonf3iatlceyy0qdax2imsanjcadoehqgdxe5zy3jlrbw9ma3iaunzluichuueo5pldh2e6lh8xkrawvy8q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 328px; width: 326px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">比如说<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 170, 214);">「讼卦」</span></strong></span>。它的爻辞讲了这样一个故事：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">因为同僚倾轧，某君把一个重要的差事办砸了。如果他就此罢休，上面骂几句，底下人发几句牢骚，这事也就过去了。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">但他不服气，去找上司那告状。结果上司没有站在他一边，还差点要追杀他。幸亏他半路逃走，在乡亲们的掩护下，侥幸逃生。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">接下来他动心忍性，砥砺自己的贞操，结果也还好。此时如果他还要出来做官，就会一事无成。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">但故事没完。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;">过了一段时间之后，他又去新领导那抱怨。这次他又失败了。回来之后他决定安守本分，彻底改变自己。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">很多年之后，他又没忍住，又去找新领导了。这次好，遇上公正的新领导，给他平反了，还把他推荐给皇帝，让他为皇帝效力。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">但一切不幸由此而来。皇上虽然也重用他，赏赐金腰带，可因为这么多年他一直在告状，得罪得人太多了。这些小人轮番向皇帝进谗言，把他的职位又给夺走了。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appXJ0BcLXr3494/image/ueditor/34643700_1553662310.cn/mmbiz_png/3mfm1joonf3ukb7h9ghjm8r24uankbt8w4eb91qfvrnpz6ticichtzlg373xgcjipiw9yjqe8vybspaoqfgnay7q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 225px; width: 556px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">「讼卦」的这个卦辞告诉我们，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">「利见大人，不利涉大川（激流的大河）」。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">翻译成大白话就是：如果遇上公正的新领导，容易有成就，如果要做很危险的事，会很不利。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">如果你在做的事，没有「大人」，只有「大河」，这样的事最好不要做，越坚持越容易一败涂地。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">《易经》最高的智慧，是辅助我们做选择，计算赢面：进还是退，尝试还是等待，冒险还是观望……</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">在人生的关键节点，我们不能错失良机，更不能胡乱出击。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">这本书不仅有大智慧和大格局，还是儒家、道家世界观、人生智慧的思想源泉，国学经典里的皇冠。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">《易经》是儒家经典之首，不仅有孔子做传，还有历代先贤朱熹、邵雍、虞翻、李光地等人做专门研究。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">不仅曾国藩从《需卦》中得到了进退之道，甚至孔子毕生所学，也要出自《乾卦》；老子毕生所学，更是源于《坤卦》。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 20px;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">2&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">课程亮点</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">在国学经典中，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">《易经》又最让人望而却步，因为这本书的文字完全看不懂。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">我在人民大学攻读硕士期间，开始钻研《易经》，又在台湾访学期间读了上万本古籍。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">我发现，《易经》里面那些晦涩难懂的卦辞、爻辞本质上都是剧本，完全可以用讲故事的方式呈现出来。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">在这门课程里，我会把<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(61, 170, 214);">易经64卦的卦辞用讲故事的方式讲出来，告别不知所云的文言文。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appXJ0BcLXr3494/image/ueditor/45565300_1553662310.cn/mmbiz_jpg/3mfm1joonf0phkhxeofowvhx70gnxfoq5avdgpnctt0x5mtdiktw7xruibe2ibica7s8m5p5vwb8eoucqwlwih7pq/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">听故事，学道理。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">我还会把这里面最重要的选择节点拿出来分析，提炼成心法，分享给你。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">剖析智者事业与情感的得失，提炼方法，让你持续地效仿、学习、积累，执行，帮助你掌握智者的人生经验，打开更广阔的人生视角。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">在过去两年，我在「十点课堂」开设过四门课程，包括三部传记课，上百个人物传记故事，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">还有一部完整的「曾国藩」解读课程。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p class="p1" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">对我来说，这门课最重要的使命是把《易经》里面的道理结合我们现代人需要的情商、沟通、人际关系、做选择的心法，把易经的道理变成对我们今天每个普通人都有用的心法。</span></p><p class="p1" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p class="p1" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;">这门课我不想单纯地讲卦理，我还会讲解许多不错的传记，结合易经的心法，把运用这个心法最成功的人物案例分享给你。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">这门易经课，你将得到：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">· 用听故事的方式理解《易经》里面的全部智慧</em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">· 收获64个关于处世、情商、沟通和做选择的心法</em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">· 还能不定期听到传记故事。</em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;">3</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-s